puha
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:2
Definition:sowthistle (as a green vegetable; Maori cabbage)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:also rauriki
Pronunciation:
Notes: also rauriki		ca1935 Havelock Marlborough puha [pu:a:], Maori cabbage, sowthistle.
